data.title: Famous People Born in July 1961
data.meta_description: Celebrate the birthdays of 66 famous people, historical figures and celebrities born in July 1961 like Diana Spencer, Carl Lewis and Toby Keith.
data.text:
Carl Lewis

American athlete (Olympic gold 100m 1984, 88; 200m 1984; 4x100m relay 1984, 92; long jump 1984, 88, 92, 96), born in Birmingham, Alabama
